# Cursor project rules pointer

**Canonical agent policy:** `AGENTS.md` (source of truth). Cursor always-on mirrors live in `.cursor/rules/`.

Do **not** replace or overwrite `AGENTS.md` with harness boilerplate.

Optional harness collateral (sidecar only, not policy):

- `agent-harnesses/data-intensive/` — batch/data-processing templates when explicitly relevant
- `.cursor/rules/harness.mdc` — short pointer (`alwaysApply: false`)

Stack: **pnpm 9** only. Never use npm or yarn.
